The weather in Jo burg is cooling off, which means you should be thinking strategically about comfort and making for Chocoloza at Milpark s 44 Stanley Avenue.Owner Vicki Bain lived in Belgium for years, and made a career leap from working in the world of lotteries to training as a chocolatier there.She s now returned home to offer the good people of the Golden City dainty cocoa delights and seven kinds of hot chocolate. Yes, you read right seven.